---
permalink: "/_admin/index.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <title>DK App Tools Admin</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #090a0b;
      --panel: rgba(24, 26, 30, 0.94);
      --panel-soft: rgba(31, 34, 39, 0.82);
      --border: rgba(220, 174, 75, 0.22);
      --border-soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --gold: #d6a83d;
      --gold-soft: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.16);
      --text: #f2eee5;
      --muted: #aaa59a;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --safe: #7bd88f;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.14), transparent 34rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08), transparent 30rem),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #070809, #101216 55%, #08090a);
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.28;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.4) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 22px 22px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 85%);
    }

    .shell {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 0 44px;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .mark {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: var(--gold);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.18), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03));
      box-shadow: 0 18px 70px rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.14);
    }

    .access-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.28);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--safe);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30, 33, 38, 0.92), rgba(18, 20, 23, 0.92));
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.36);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-main {
      padding: 30px;
      border-color: var(--border);
    }

    .kicker {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 760px;
      font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 76px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    }

    .lead {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .warning {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.24);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: var(--gold-soft);
      color: #f6e4b2;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .side-card {
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      align-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .status-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .status-list li {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .status-list strong {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .toolbar {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .button {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .button[disabled] {
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.54;
      filter: grayscale(0.2);
    }

    .mock-table {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
    }

    .row-title {
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .row-meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.12);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .disabled-note {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-mock {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .input-mock {
      padding: 13px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .hero,
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .topbar {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="mark">DK</div>
        <div>
          <div>DK App Tools Admin</div>
          <small style="color: var(--muted);">Вътрешен панел</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="access-pill">Защитено с Cloudflare Access</div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="card hero-main">
        <div class="kicker">Admin preview</div>
        <h1>Панел за статии и съдържание.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Това е първа защитена mock версия на бъдещия български admin панел.
          Реални write функции още няма. Save Draft и Publish са умишлено изключени,
          докато не бъде добавен server-side backend.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="card side-card">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">Security state</div>
          <ul class="status-list">
            <li><span>Hostname</span><strong>admin.dkapptools.com</strong></li>
            <li><span>Access</span><strong>Cloudflare</strong></li>
            <li><span>Write backend</span><strong>Not connected</strong></li>
            <li><span>Publish</span><strong>Disabled</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="warning">
          Няма GitHub token в browser-а. Няма публичен Publish бутон. Няма реално записване.
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card section">
        <h2>Статии</h2>
        <div class="toolbar">
          <button class="button" disabled>Нова статия</button>
          <button class="button" disabled>Запази чернова</button>
          <button class="button" disabled>Публикувай</button>
        </div>

        <div class="mock-table">
          <div class="row">
            <div>
              <div class="row-title">Why offline-first security still matters</div>
              <div class="row-meta">Mock preview • published article</div>
            </div>
            <span class="badge">Published</span>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div>
              <div class="row-title">How local file vaults protect privacy</div>
              <div class="row-meta">Mock preview • published article</div>
            </div>
            <span class="badge">Published</span>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div>
              <div class="row-title">Нова статия за бъдещ редактор</div>
              <div class="row-meta">Mock draft • backend not connected</div>
            </div>
            <span class="badge">Draft mock</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="disabled-note">
          Тази секция е само визуален прототип. Реалното създаване, редактиране и публикуване
          ще се включи чак след protected server-side write endpoint.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card section">
        <h2>Редактор</h2>
        <div class="form-mock">
          <div class="input-mock">Заглавие на статията</div>
          <div class="input-mock">Slug / URL</div>
          <div class="input-mock">Card image + alt text</div>
          <div class="input-mock">Structured blocks: paragraph, heading, image, callout</div>
          <div class="input-mock">Preview panel</div>
        </div>

        <p class="disabled-note">
          Следващата реална backend фаза ще валидира полетата server-side и ще записва
          markdown/image файлове без да излага credentials в public JavaScript.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      DK App Tools Admin • Protected mock UI • No write operations enabled
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
